ls0 ws0">it.&quot;—&quot;Fresh Light </div><div class="t m514 x16 h94 y97d ff6 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">from the Ancient Monuments.&quot; pages 24, 25. </div><div class="t m3d5 x6b h5f y207c ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE PAPACY&apos;S CLAIM </div><div class="t m149 x5d h5f y14b7 ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m3b5 x29 h94 y14b7 ff6 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Ques. </div><div class="t m2916 x35 h5f y14b7 ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Which is the Sabbath day? </div><div class="t mc5b x29 h94 y2031 ff6 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Ans. </div><div class="t mc47 x3f h5f y2031 ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Saturday is the Sabbath day. </div><div class="t m6c8 x29 h94 yd72 ff6 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Ques. </div><div class="t m1e46 x35 h5f y11ef ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why do we observe Sunday instead of Saturday? </div><div class="t m2dbd x29 h94 ya8e ff6 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Ans. </div><div class="t mffc x3f h5f ya8e ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We observe Sunday instead of Saturday because the ,Catholic </div><div class="t m2916 x3e h5f y7d3 ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Church, in the Council of Laodicea (A. D. 336), transferred the solemnity </div><div class="t m1b11 x3e h5f y959 ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">from Saturday to Sunday.&quot;—&quot;The </div><div class="t m115d x68 h94 y56b ff6 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Convert&apos;s Catechism of Catholic Doctrine,&quot; </div><div class="t m2f3 x3e h94 y113d ff6 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 50. </div><div class="t mf52 x4e h15 yada ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lesson 12— Separation from Babylon </div><div class="t m2de x42 h5f yc05 ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DECEMBER </div><div class="t m2e8 x2a h4 yf07 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">17, 1921 </div><div class="t ma67 x69 h4 y106d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Daily Study Outline </div><div class="t m7a0 x16 h7b yf3d ff1 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m29e4 x48 h7b y1236 ff1 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Study synopsis, paragraphs 4. Questions 9-16; note 2. </div><div class="